---
title: Pork Fajitas with Blistered Peppers and Sour Cream
description: When in doubt, Tex-Mex is always the answer. We’ve swapped out beef for pork but kept the classic nutritious and colorful veggies. And fear not, our spice blend is mild enough for everyone to enjoy, especially when a dollop (or two) of sour cream is involved.
